{"tid":1453553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論] 有邊個中資航空嘅機票艙等係可以免費取消？","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:55:01.000Z","uid":73381,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f55de50a3312717b4cc4356d2ca874bbaf61ca6","tid":1453553,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:35:44.000Z","msg":"不嬲支持開中資航空公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但今次我驚我去到離境大堂突然間有急事出發唔到 所以想搵可以免費取消嘅機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8bde5069805b04ef2e006c1bead94c2fb1abdc","tid":1453553,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:36:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"192c6fb1ddc184f9b3f7fd7eac7152670a9c8b92","tid":1453553,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2598014b46bc177f18e0d55fcd56a8c07b234cc8","tid":1453553,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:39:46.000Z","msg":"有無人知"},{"pid":"90acf02d7ee0896c8f478a20c59dacd5ae4523d7","tid":1453553,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:40:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd7fbab3081d5efbd9f4c7ca6a828d6437648b6c","tid":1453553,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"from 頭大大機師fb<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果我突然有事不想飛，取消航班手續費是多少呢？<br />\n是零啊！<br />\n是零啊！<br />\n是零啊！</span><br />\n<br />\n因為基本上如果你買<span style=\"color: red;\">全費(Full Fare)機票</span>，不論頭等、商務或者經濟，即使你登機後有任何理由要取消航班，航空均沒有權阻止，並且可以全費退回。<br />\n(國泰，澳洲航空適用，其他航空公司請於購票前查詢清楚。)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想知中資航空公司係唔係都係一樣？"},{"pid":"8a3da41b28f7e909a539f3c1e7a790eaba5770fc","tid":1453553,"uid":2959,